        Summary

                
        
            
            
                
                    
                    
                        
                            Abstract: 
                            Reconstructed solar total and background irradiances. 
 11-yr Tootal Solar Irradiance (TSI) component since 1874 is from Foukal and 
 Lean: earlier from Hoyt Sunspot Groups 
 Background Brightness component is Average Hoyt Group Count per cycle 
 
 Data in 1995, 1996 & 1997 appended May 98.     
                        

                    
                    
                
            

            

        
    


                      
            
            
            










    
